+- `docs/source/functional-spec.md` M04-FR-005 through M04-FR-007
+- `docs/source/api-contracts.md` §§6-8 and §§22-24
+- `docs/source/codebase-design.md` §§22.1, 26.1-27.1, and §§42.1-42.3
