+5. Append newest-first findings, create or sharpen executable corrective slices for significant issues, and sharpen the next one or two Not Started slices using already-opened sources.
+6. Run documentation/queue and applicable project quality gates; retain logs and prepare changed-files, risk, review packet, final summary, state, progress, handoff, and architecture-review status artifacts.
+
+Production code will not be modified.
